headline: Bio-Techne   Launches Simple   Plex   Ultra-Sensitive   Assays on Ella   Platform to Enable   Femtogram-Level   Detection of Neurological Biomarkers
summary: Bio-Techne Corporation (NASDAQ: TECH), a global provider of life science tools, reagents, and diagnostic products, today announced the launch of Simple Plex Ultra-Sensitive Assays on the Ella automated benchtop platform.
